public class SearchTask
extends android.support.v4.content.AsyncTaskLoader<java.util.List<java.lang.String>>

Created by na389 on 9/30/14. Loader used to handle the autocomplete feature of the keyword and location in main search screen. It makes the call gets the results and converts it to corresponding data model so that it can be used within the implementation.
